ges-Article","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" articles for more information about colors and images."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"View-styles","text":"View styles","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit defines custom styles for its various view. For instance, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Keyboard","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Keyboard\/Button","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view has a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Keyboard\/ButtonStyle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" that can be applied with the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/SwiftUI\/View\/keyboardButtonStyle(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" view modifier."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Most views have static, standard styles that can be replaced by custom styles to change the global default style for that particular view."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"How to create a custom style provider","anchor":"How-to-create-a-custom-style-provider"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can create a custom style provider to customize any style in any way you want. You can implement ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyleProvider","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" from scratch, or inherit and customize "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyle\/StandardProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inli